name: In The Cave Of The Mountain Demon King (Special Edition)
description: Mothtasia presents an Offical NFT for the 69 Special Editions of our song "In The Cave Of The Mountain Demon King" from our first album "Chrysalis Transition" - further immortalizing the legacy of "Harold" the family heirloom violin - among the first violins made in the 2nd Industrial Revolution, Pre-WWI, taken out of storage and humidity decay to create the violin parts of this music.
